Edit the files standard.phml, editing.phtml and viewing.phtml in layouts.

Add 1 <div id="top"> after <body> and 1 <div id="bottom"> before </body> to the 3 layouts:

<body>
<div id="top"></div>
...
<div id="bottom">
<div id="trees"></div>
<div id="forest"></div>
<div id="grass"></div>
</div>
</body>

Change $theme in includes/config.inc to 'winter':

$theme='winter';

